            "id": 6143288,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 甲骨文(ORCL-US)大漲5.03%，報234.21美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)截至台北時間06日03:28股價上漲11.21美元，報234.21美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量11,067,893（股），盤中最高價234.21美元、最低價225.89美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.52%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.4%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.6%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-7.21%</li> <li>近 1 月：-11.69%</li> <li>近 3 月：+32.66%</li> <li>近 6 月：+41.61%</li> <li>今年以來：+33.82%</li></ul></section></main>",
